johto_pokedex.name: Girafarig
johto_pokedex.description: Its tail has a small brain of its own. It will bite you if you get too close.

johto_pokedex.name: Pineco
johto_pokedex.description: It looks like a pinecone. It waits for flying insect prey to come near it, then sprays them with a gooey fluid.

johto_pokedex.name: Forretress
johto_pokedex.description: It is encased in a steel-hard shell. Its startled eyes are visible through a crack in the shell.

johto_pokedex.name: Dunsparce
johto_pokedex.description: When spotted, it escapes backward by digging into the ground with its tail. It can float just slightly.

johto_pokedex.name: Gligar
johto_pokedex.description: It glides without making a single sound. It clings to its prey's face, then jabs the surprised victim with its poisonous tail.
johto_pokedex.evolution: Evolves into Gliscor while holding a Razor Fang at night.

johto_pokedex.name: Steelix
johto_pokedex.description: The iron scraps it eats builds up its body, making it harder than diamond.

johto_pokedex.name: Snubbull
johto_pokedex.description: It looks ferocious, but it is actually kind and affectionate. It is very popular among women.

johto_pokedex.name: Granbull
johto_pokedex.description: It has a particularly vicious bite. It is timid in spite of its looks. It is a popular pet.

johto_pokedex.name: Qwilfish
johto_pokedex.description: To fire its poison spikes, it must inflate its body by drinking over 2.6 gallons of water all at once.

johto_pokedex.name: Scizor
johto_pokedex.description: It has a steel-hard body. It intimidates foes by upraising its eye-patterned pincers.

johto_pokedex.name: Shuckle
johto_pokedex.description: The berries stored in its jar-like shell ferment and become a delicious juice.

johto_pokedex.name: Heracross
johto_pokedex.description: This powerful Pokémon thrusts its prized horn under its enemies' bellies, then lifts and throws them.

johto_pokedex.name: Sneasel
johto_pokedex.description: It has a cunning nature. A Sneasel will not hesitate to steal eggs from unguarded nests.
johto_pokedex.evolution: Evolves into Weavile while holding a Razor Claw at night.

johto_pokedex.name: Teddiursa
johto_pokedex.description: It always licks honey. Its palm tastes sweet because of the honey it has absorbed.

johto_pokedex.name: Ursaring
johto_pokedex.description: It is a good climber, but it prefers to snap trees with its forelegs and eat fallen berries.
johto_pokedex.evolution: Evolves into Ursaluna with a Peat Block during a full moon.

johto_pokedex.name: Slugma
johto_pokedex.description: Its body is made of magma. If it doesn't keep moving, its body will cool and harden.

johto_pokedex.name: Magcargo
johto_pokedex.description: Its body temperature is roughly 18,000 degrees Fahrenheit. Flames spout from gaps in its shell.

johto_pokedex.name: Swinub
johto_pokedex.description: It rubs its snout on the ground to find and dig up food. It sometimes discovers hot springs.

johto_pokedex.name: Piloswine
johto_pokedex.description: Covered by a shaggy coat, it is strong against the cold. Its tusks of ice thicken when it snows.
johto_pokedex.evolution: Evolves into Mamoswine after learning Ancient Power.

johto_pokedex.name: Corsola
johto_pokedex.description: It continuously sheds and grows. The tip of its head is prized as a treasure for its beauty.

johto_pokedex.name: Remoraid
johto_pokedex.description: It clings to the fins of Mantine and eats whatever is left behind. It can shoot water like a pistol.

johto_pokedex.name: Octillery
johto_pokedex.description: It has a reference for things with holes. It often sneaks into holes in rocks and stays there.

johto_pokedex.name: Delibird
johto_pokedex.description: It carries food all day long. It has been known to share its food with people lost in the mountains.

johto_pokedex.name: Mantine
johto_pokedex.description: As it majestically swims, it doesn't care if Remoraid attach to it for leftover food.

johto_pokedex.name: Skarmory
johto_pokedex.description: Its tough wings are actually hollow and light, allowing it to fly freely in the sky.

johto_pokedex.name: Houndour
johto_pokedex.description: It is smart enough to hunt in packs. It uses a variety of cries to corner its prey.

johto_pokedex.name: Houndoom
johto_pokedex.description: The flames it breathes when angry contain toxins. If they cause a burn, it will hurt forever.

johto_pokedex.name: Kingdra
johto_pokedex.description: It is said that it hides in underwater caves. It can create whirlpools by yawning.

johto_pokedex.name: Phanpy
johto_pokedex.description: It is strong despite its small size. It can easily carry a person on its back.

johto_pokedex.name: Donphan
johto_pokedex.description: The longer and bigger its tusks, the higher its rank in the herd. The tusks take a long time to grow.

johto_pokedex.name: Porygon2
johto_pokedex.description: It was created by humans using the latest technology. It may occasionally show motions that were not programmed.
johto_pokedex.evolution: Evolves into Porygon-Z via trade while holding a Dubious Disc.

johto_pokedex.name: Stantler
johto_pokedex.description: The curved antlers subtly change the flow of air to create a strange space where reality is distorted.
johto_pokedex.evolution: Evolves into Wyrdeer after using Psyshield Bash in the Agile Style 20 times.

johto_pokedex.name: Smeargle
johto_pokedex.description: The color of the mysterious fluid secreted from its tail is predetermined for each Smeargle.

johto_pokedex.name: Tyrogue
johto_pokedex.description: It is always bursting with energy. To make itself stronger, it will challenge any foe, no matter how much bigger it is.
johto_pokedex.evolution: Evolves into Hitmonlee (Attack > Defense), Hitmonchan (Defense > Attack), or Hitmontop (Attack = Defense).

johto_pokedex.name: Hitmontop
johto_pokedex.description: It fights while spinning like a top. The centrifugal force boosts its destructive power by ten.

johto_pokedex.name: Smoochum
johto_pokedex.description: Its lips are the most sensitive part of its body. It uses them to inspect new things.

johto_pokedex.name: Elekid
johto_pokedex.description: It rotates its arms to generate electricity, but it tires easily, so it charges up only a little.

johto_pokedex.name: Magby
johto_pokedex.description: It is found in volcanic craters. Its body temperature is over 1,100 degrees Fahrenheit.

johto_pokedex.name: Miltank
johto_pokedex.description: Its milk is packed with nutrition, making it the ultimate beverage for the sick or weary.

johto_pokedex.name: Blissey
johto_pokedex.description: Anyone who takes even one bite of Blissey's egg becomes unfailingly caring and pleasant to everyone.

johto_pokedex.name: Raikou
johto_pokedex.description: It is said to have descended with lightning. It can fire thunderbolts from the rain clouds on its back.

johto_pokedex.name: Entei
johto_pokedex.description: A Pokémon that races across the land. It is said that one is born every time a new volcano appears.

johto_pokedex.name: Suicune
johto_pokedex.description: It travels across the land, purifying polluted water. It moves together with the north wind.

johto_pokedex.name: Larvitar
johto_pokedex.description: A Pokémon that eats soil. After it has eaten a large mountain, it will fall asleep so it can grow.

johto_pokedex.name: Pupitar
johto_pokedex.description: Its shell is as hard as bedrock. It is a wildly rampaging Pokémon that destroys mountains.

johto_pokedex.name: Tyranitar
johto_pokedex.description: In just one of its mighty hands, it has the power to make the ground shake and mountains crumble.

johto_pokedex.name: Lugia
johto_pokedex.description: It is said that it quietly spends its time deep at the bottom of the sea because its powers are too strong.

johto_pokedex.name: Ho-Oh
johto_pokedex.description: It is said that anyone who sees it is promised eternal happiness. It has seven-colored wings.

johto_pokedex.name: Celebi
johto_pokedex.description: This Pokémon came from the future by crossing over time. It is thought that so long as Celebi appears, a bright and shining future awaits us.
